Usage: reportFootPrint [-help] [<footprint>] [-dontTouchNUse]
                       [-outfile <string>]

-help                 # Prints out the command usage
<footprint>           # to report a specific footprint (string, optional)
-dontTouchNUse        # print dont_touch and dont_true cells (bool, optional)
-outfile <string>     # output file name (string, optional)